## Verdict

**NEEDS WORK**

Two HIGH findings (A4b `isFirst` guard omission causes pure image-slide visual regression; A3d TitleBlock `marginBottom` misdescribed as NEU) will cause implementation bugs that are not caught by tsc alone and will appear as Codex R1 findings. Three MEDIUM findings (A5d TypeScript type guard, E1/E2 missing test cases, A3b synthesis gap) will each produce Codex findings. Address all HIGH and MEDIUM items before implementation starts.
